{"tid":2131411,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"字節跳動股東擬洽購TikTok　估值3900億","createTime":"2020-07-30T00:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T00:50:40.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4bc9f212b04e84a598319d6f6222c2ada56c699d","tid":2131411,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2020/07/30/2535597_060414bb4232cc1cf2a38981a7e99cde_320.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2020%2F07%2F30%2F2535597_060414bb4232cc1cf2a38981a7e99cde_320.png&h=1676f155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n路透引述消息人士稱，中國短視頻平台抖音國際版TikTok的母公司字節跳動(ByteDance)，部分股東尋求收購TikTok，交易估值為500億美元(3900億港元)，遠高於美國同類企業Snap的企業估值。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧及華府多名官員近期對TikTok作出嚴厲批評，聲稱考慮禁止TikTok涉足美國市場。<br />\n<br />\n根據報道，包括Sequoia、General Atlantic等美國基金在內的字節跳動部分股東提議，把TikTok控制權轉至他們手上，交易作價以500億美元為估值基準。同時，有其他財團也表達收購TikTok的意願。字節跳動正在考慮TikTok未來安排。<br />\n<br />\n暫時不確定字節跳動創辦人兼行政總裁張一鳴是否同意轉讓TikTok。有字節跳動管理層近期表示，TikTok估值超過500億美元。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士稱，字節跳動也考慮非整體出售TikTok，只出售TikTok美國業務。暫時不確定美國業務的獨立估值多少。<br />\n<br />\n字節跳動、TikTok、Sequoia與General Atlantic拒評上述消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2535597/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F2535597%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhJIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=9f91a085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2535597/</a>"},{"pid":"da258f92dda8ccbdb785877964d2f27091fc4658","tid":2131411,"uid":117318,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:30:04.000Z","msg":"算啦，抖陰點賣都係整唔甩陣𨳍味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d310ab0dabdbfe3ff29d9ef700fab51555285b24","tid":2131411,"uid":39710,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:30:59.000Z","msg":"左手交右手咪又係支那嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb1ccadecf8c8d8fdb3da9237d865de50017953","tid":2131411,"uid":54528,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:41:03.000Z","msg":"等睇美帝ban tiktok"},{"pid":"1c9a897b8769e599f0050136bf707eda87ea513f","tid":2131411,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:41:20.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"1c377ee4c4330f6bc21d35300356481ac98874f7","tid":2131411,"uid":2230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:49:26.000Z","msg":"買個班咪又係中資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de62c8de363a4659066238fd8dc4081da83855c","tid":2131411,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:50:15.000Z","msg":"扮晒野，以為老美傻既？"},{"pid":"3019cac0732a130f21b97bcf61a2724c6ca01c81","tid":2131411,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Zoom 都話係美資"}]}